-- Huntsman to Increase Global Prices for Titanium-Dioxide Pigments
-- B y   J a c k   K a s k e y
-- 2013-02-20T21:48:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-20/huntsman-to-increase-global-prices-for-titanium-dioxide-pigments.html
Huntsman Corp., the third-biggest
producer of titanium-dioxide pigment, said it will increase
global prices for the whitening chemical effective March 15.  It will raise prices in Europe by 230 euros or $300 a ton,
the U.S. company said today in a  statement  on its website.
Prices will increase 10 U.S. cents or 10 Canadian cents a pound
in North America, and by $300 a ton in Africa, the Middle East
and the Asia-Pacific region.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jack Kaskey in Houston at 
